openstm32sw README

The aim is to provide both Open Source software and hardware for STM32. 
This is the software repository.

This repository grew from a discussion thread on LeafLabs Maple forum:
http://forums.leaflabs.com/topic.php?id=1303

It was triggered by ala42 who had released a first cut at libmaple for STM32F4:
http://forums.leaflabs.com/topic.php?id=1268&page=2#post-7828

We are aiming to maintain compatibility with LeafLabs Maple software API

LeafLabs announced that they are collaborating with Wiring
http://leaflabs.com/2011/11/were-teaming-up-with-wiring/

Hence openstm32 should have some compatibility with the Wiring Framework.


sub-directories:

stm32f4 - ala42's stm32f4 fork of libmaple and maple bootloader